title: About
text:
This blog was generated to manage my blogs.
There are two purposes for achieving something here.

First
I will get definitions of any subjects and organize that in my words.
It is important to understand those information if I want to research exactly and improve myself.


Second
I will brief my past and present researches.
Overall, this blog will be the essential step for developing my skills.
